gov.usgs.volcanoes.swarm.data.seedLink.orfeus

Class BaseSLClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.usgs.volcanoes.swarm.data.seedLink.orfeus.BaseSLClient
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Runnable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SeedLinkClient

    public class BaseSLClient
extends Object
implements Runnable
    Base class to create and use a connection to a SeedLink server using a SeedLinkConnection object. A new SeedLink application can be created by subclassing BaseSLClient and overriding at least the packetHandler method of BaseSLClient.
    See Also:
    nl.knmi.orfeus.seedlink.client.SLClient.
